    "body" : "<p>You can use the <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/apidocs/org/apache/commons/lang3/StringUtils.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">StringUtils</a> class from <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Apache Commons Lang</a> like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>StringUtils.stripStart(yourString,\"0\");\n</code></pre>\n"
